Reflex Save : 
0 : container TAG gets used to index inventory. container with the same tag share the same inventory

2 : player gets used as the index. use this to make player-vaults. same container will yield a different inventory based on the opener


Will Save : 
Set this to equal the maximum number of items allowed in the saddlebags

0: This will have a default of 250 items maximum.

Any other number for a will save will have that many items as the limit in the saddlebag.  NOTE:  Stacked items count as one item.
